snippet.title: Necronator: Dead Wrong Launch Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Necronator: Dead Wrong launches out of Early Access with a massive new content update! Conquer the realms of the living in the first deckbuilding RTS. Get it on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1144970/Necronator_Dead_Wrong/


It's time for a masterclass in world domination from Chubat! Learn how to dominate the lands of the living by building a deck of undead minions and unleash them in micro-RTS battles.


Necronator: Dead Wrong is available on PC:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1144970/Necronator_Dead_Wrong/
Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/necronator-dead-wrong


Follow us on Twitter!
Modern Wolf: https://twitter.com/ModernWolfLtd
Toge Productions: https://twitter.com/togeproductions



#necronator #deckbuilding #rts #necronatordeadwrong
